    "updated_at": "2016-08-11T10:41:41Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Honestly not having an ability/order window when we have orders like Guard, Force fire, Lay mines, Transform etc is a clusterfuck from a usability standpoint.\nJust as an example many users didn't even know you could lay down a minefield with the minelayer by holding down control and clicking twice.\n\nSure double clicking can also be used but what about the 5 other things that we could add to control infantry, do we just hide them behind other arbitrary button clicks and never show them to new players just because the UI isn't \"pure\".\n\nLiterally every other stragety game I have played except those from the early Cnc series have the windows, age of empires, starcraft, warcraft, supreme commander etc.\n"
  },
